data.description: Great home in a great location! This home boasts many recent renovations including a brand-new deck and addition of a door off the dining room, a new heat pump, recently refinished floors, replacement windows, new sliding glass door downstairs, new flooring downstairs, recently resealed driveway & fresh paint throughout. It is situated on a large, level lot with mature trees providing privacy. Convenient to Radford University, Belle Heth Elementary, and only 1 mile from Radford High School.
